com.joliciel.talismane.posTagger

Interface PosTagger

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    NonDeterministicPosTagger
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ForwardStatisticalPosTagger

    public interface PosTagger
    The PosTagger's task is to add part-of-speech tags to words within a sentence. More specifically, the tagSentence(TokenSequence) method takes a TokenSequence as input and produces a PosTagSequence, which extends a List of PosTaggedToken.
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static java.lang.String LEMMA_ATTRIBUTE
      If this attribute is added to a Token via Token.addAttribute(String, TokenAttribute) (typically using a RegexAnnotator), and the value of this attribute is "originalLower", then the token's lemma will be set to the value provided.
      static java.lang.String LEMMA_TYPE_ATTRIBUTE
      If this attribute is added to a Token via Token.addAttribute(String, TokenAttribute) (typically using a RegexAnnotator), and the value of this attribute is "originalLower", then the token's lemma will be set to the original value, forced into lowercase.
      static java.lang.String POS_TAG_ATTRIBUTE
      If this attribute is added to a Token via Token.addAttribute(String, TokenAttribute) (typically using a RegexAnnotator), the token in question will get the pos-tag in the attribute value assigned to it without consulting the statistical model.

    • Field Detail

      • POS_TAG_ATTRIBUTE

        static final java.lang.String POS_TAG_ATTRIBUTE
        If this attribute is added to a Token via Token.addAttribute(String, TokenAttribute) (typically using a RegexAnnotator), the token in question will get the pos-tag in the attribute value assigned to it without consulting the statistical model. This is an alternative to using pos-tagger rules.

        Constant Field Values
